Wild Spinach, Purslane, Hyssop, Blue Flag, Currants, Wild Strawberries, Tansy. Paige Dansinger, 2017

Prototype drawings of a VR Game. Native Ojibwe Storyteller shares her memories of plants used for edible, medicinal, or poison. This VR Herbal Walk Game is a collaboration with Beth Hedman Dodds and Hattie Ball. Directed by Paige Dansinger, Better World Museum.
